This might also explain in part why the Russians held off on trying to foment conflict with North Korea or Iran, and why China and Russia ignored Obama's "diplomatic efforts" to stop Syria and North Korea from obtaining WMDs. If both knew the U.S. Government has a problem with infiltration from Russian and Chinese spies, and both knew Russian propaganda outlets like InfoWars, Breitbart, Rush Limbaugh, Laura Ingraham, Sean Hannity, and others were gaining a foothold in U.S. media, they could predict that the U.S. was about to get "regime changed," and any consequences for their actions would be short-lived.
